{% comment %}
fix-tests — standalone base view. Block contract mirrors the other
shipped stories (status / heading / body / choices / footer) so any room
composes the same chrome. Operator-facing voice: terse, declarative.
{% endcomment %}
{% block status %}fix-tests  ·  cycle {{ world.cycle }}/{{ world.max_cycles }}  ·  {% if world.tests_passed %}green{% else %}red{% endif %}{% if world.outcome %}  ·  {{ world.outcome }}{% endif %}{% endblock %}

{% block heading %}{{ state.description }}{% endblock %}

{% block body %}{% endblock %}

{% block choices %}{% endblock %}
{% block footer %}{% endblock %}
